"SD card images, for embedded systems such as Raspberry Pi. These files must "
"be uncompressed and written as a raw image to an SD card, from which the "
"board will boot."
msgstr "SD卡镜像，用于树莓派等嵌入式系统。这些文件必须解压缩并以原始镜像的形式写入SD卡，从中启动板子。"

#. type: Plain text
